  "name": "Mordenkainen's Armament",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "source": {
      "book": "Materia"
    },
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a weapon-shaped plane of force that hovers within range. It lasts for the duration.</p><p>When the weapon appears, you make a melee spell attack against a target of your choice within 5 feet of the weapon. On a hit, the target takes [[/r 3d10]] force damage. Until the spell ends, you can use a bonus action on each of your turns to move the weapon up to 60 feet to a spot you can see and repeat this attack against the same target or a different one.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 8th level or higher, the damage increases by [[/r 1d10]] for each slot level above 7th.</p>",
